     - Target assets are recalculated monthly
     - Evidence reflects actual activity for the reporting period
     - API consumers are consumer-driven and not schedule-driven
     - SLAs are measured at the provisioning boundary (table/view availability), not individual API calls

4. Source Asset Clean-Up
   - Any assets that do not flow into TechADS should be removed from scope to avoid confusion during QA review.

